<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٤ص٦١:</span> قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى: <span class="c3">{وَكَمْ مِنْ قَرْيَةٍ أَهْلَكْنَاهَا فَجَاءَهَا بَأْسُنَا بَيَاتًا أَوْ هُمْ قَائِلُونَ}</span> <span class="c4">[الأعراف: ٤]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c3">{بَيَاتًا}</span>: <span class="c2">«لَيْلًا»</span>،<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c3">{لَنُبَيِّتَنَّهُ}</span> <span class="c4">[النمل: ٤٩]</span>: <span class="c2">«لَيْلًا»</span>،<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
